<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BEBURAS — Global Recruitment 2026</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

        :root {
            --bg:        #020d18;
            --bg2:       #041525;
            --surface:   rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            --surface2:  rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            --blue:      #4A90E2;
            --blue-dim:  rgba(74,144,226,0.18);
            --blue-glow: rgba(74,144,226,0.08);
            --border:    rgba(74,144,226,0.18);
            --border-w:  rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            --white:     #f0ede8;
            --muted:     rgba(240,237,232,0.55);
            --dimmer:    rgba(240,237,232,0.35);
            --gold:      #c9a84c;
            --gold-dim:  rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ─── LOGO WATERMARK ─── */
        .logo-watermark {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 30px; /* Logo będzie w lewym dolnym rogu. Zmień na 'right: 30px', jeśli chcesz w prawym */
            width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            opacity: 0.4; /* Domyślna przezroczystość */
            z-index: 9999;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .logo-watermark:hover {
            opacity: 0.7; /* Rozjaśnienie po najechaniu */
        }

        /* ─── PAGE ─── */
        .page {
            max-width: 1320px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 80px 60px 100px;
        }

        /* ─── HEADER ─── */
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 70px;
            padding-bottom: 50px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.2);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header:after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -2px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 200px;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #4A90E2, transparent);
        }

        .header-eyebrow {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--blue);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
            font-size: clamp(44px, 5vw, 64px);
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.05;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--muted);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* ─── RESZTA STYLÓW (NIE ZMIENIONA) ─── */
        
        /* ... Tutaj zostaje cała reszta Twojego oryginalnego CSSa (sekcje, statystyki, tabele itd.) ... */
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<img src="https://i.postimg.cc/qMSykWk3/logo-studio-removebg-preview-1.png" alt="BEBURAS Logo" class="logo-watermark">

<div class="page">

    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-eyebrow">Global Recruitment · 2026</div>
        <h1>BEBURAS Capital &amp;<br>Global Ventures</h1>
        <p>All positions are 100% performance-based · Remote · Global · No salary · No ceiling</p>
    </div>

    ```

